The big problem is, there is no fair way to do it. Every faction (Commish, Owners, Players, Fans) has a different POV on what constitutes fair. If Fans had their way, everyone BUT the player on their team would get suspended. If Players had their way, players would never get fined or suspended, if Owners had their way, players would play simply play for the love of the game and we fans would tithe the NFL. So talking about fair is going to get you nowhere. In the end Goodell is CEO of the NFL, only answerable to the Owners.
